title: 'Simple tape measure'
body: It's accurate as I checked with a couple of other measuring tapes. However, I was hoping to get a bright yellow one but received one which is white on the inch side and pale green on the other side. Also, most tape measures leave a blank space after the metal clip and the 0 starts after that. Not so for this one. It's an annoyance because I will have to start from the 1-inch point and measure forward. For Rs. 46, this is probably the best that you get.
